description:
Have you ever wondered about Elohim's incredible nature?
In Psalms 90:2, David beautifully expresses the timeless truth that Elohim is God from everlasting to everlasting. Join us on a journey of understanding and embracing Elohim's boundless love for each of us. Watch as Pastor Sam Neves delves into the profound message, revealing the depth of Elohim's care and desire for our best.#Shorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ #YouTubeShorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​

To watch the full video, paste this link into your browser:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OdadjgtkSjc&feature=youtu.be
